with open('3proxy.conf', 'w') as out:
    out.write('\n'.join(('allow *', 'auth none', 'proxy -a -n -p%d -e%s' %
        (HTTP_PROXY_PORT, PROXY_HOST_IP), 'socks -p%d -e%s' % (
        SOCKS4_PROXY_PORT, PROXY_HOST_IP), 'socks -p%d -e%s' % (
        SOCKS5_PROXY_PORT, PROXY_HOST_IP))))
cmd = 'test/bin/3proxy 3proxy.conf'
server = Popen(cmd, shell=True)
server.wait()
